Package com.flipkart.business

Interface AdminInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
AdminService
public interface AdminInterface
Interface for administrative functions within the system. This interface provides methods for viewing and verifying details of gym owners and gyms, as well as retrieving lists of unverified entities and general user information.
